Title: Relates to fair pricing for low-complexity, routine medical care
Summary: Relates to fair pricing for low-complexity, routine medical care to more closely align payment rates across ambulatory settings for selected services that are safe and appropriate to provide in all settings.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to fair pricing for low-complexity, routine medical care
